{"tid":1498063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求官立中學開學文宣","createTime":"2019-08-23T08:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T09:19:31.000Z","uid":145292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9ec2defa64595112da84163a3366f30491a30e","tid":1498063,"uid":145292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:49:51.000Z","msg":"我係一間官立中學學生，官立中學通常會跟足教育局指引。<br />\n我身為其中一間官立中學嘅學生，我覺得有責任去提醒我身邊嘅港豬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我想求文宣講返五大訴求比我身邊嘅港豬。<br />\n<br />\n一名偏遠地區官立中學學生"},{"pid":"f813fe267be56562e258ea454b98be645afc609f","tid":1498063,"uid":145292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:52:18.000Z","msg":"求各位收手足幫下手"},{"pid":"ea2c9ccdfad36a5e2d25aa68a713a51de59edb3c","tid":1498063,"uid":145292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"文宣組幫下我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e234b594f2bd765d283da641376ee57b7016d9","tid":1498063,"uid":44074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:16:19.000Z","msg":"lennon wall"},{"pid":"af1c5588559e5cafed2661eec2cac5ab488ac4fd","tid":1498063,"uid":145292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13e234b594f2bd765d283da641376ee57b7016d9","tid":1498063,"uid":44074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:16:19.000Z","msg":"lennon wall"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:19:31.000Z","msg":"自製連儂牆唔夠呀， 我要喺學校門口派嗰啲單張"}]}